710415f-a.title: Manhattan: 9th Avenue - 50th Street (West)
710415f-a.text:
Ninth Avenue, north from W. 50th Street, as photographed from
the dewntown "El" platform. Shown are details of track and station
at this point prior to demolition. Note the raised express portion.
This was inclined to permit the shunting of 6th Avenue trains east-
ward on W. 53rd Street.
June 6, 1940
